        "desc": "The terrace on this roof of the Guards' Office has no wall on the western side,\nnot even a rail - seems the Elf who built it is deft enough to not care about\nfalling off. Half of the terrace is protected with a wooden cover, and the\nwestern part is open. To the east a simple door leads into the house. A round,\nreliable hatch can be used to descend down.\n",
